labels: [['The restaurant has a garden room that has floor-to-ceiling panes of glass that overlook the patio, and the main dining room downstairs has hand-carved wooden replicas of the native birds of Louisiana as well as electric chandeliers, each worth $10,000, with lights that flicker and move as if they were candle flames.
